<div id="content" class="col620">


	<div class="post-135 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-male-sexuality category-masculinity category-myths-and-misconceptions category-personal-history category-politics-of-sex category-sexism tag-asking-questions tag-bad-schooling tag-culture-is-painful tag-intelligence tag-men tag-sexism-in-the-workforce tag-why-is-important tag-women clear" id="post-135">
